  <h1>Votes</h1>

  <p><strong>New 9/2/12</strong></p>

  <p>We're now experimenting with giving all Colby users the ability to upvote and downvote on posts. Votes get counted toward that user's "karma," not that individual post. Posts on The Better Announcements are now ordered by user karma, so the more bad puns you make, the <s>higher</s> lower down your posts will appear relative to everyone else.</p>
